the thieves	盜賊們
The shelf contains several types of glassware, each of which appears to be supporting several types of bacteria.	架子上擺著幾種玻璃器皿，每一種上頭似乎都養著好幾種細菌。
the shelf	架子
The shelf is dirtier than the bar only because the customers keep the bar clean with their dirty shirt sleeves.	架子比吧台還髒，純粹是因為顧客們老用髒袖子把吧台擦乾淨。
It is an ex-parrot.  It had one too many (that is to say one) Djinn Sling.  Actually, it's just pining for the fjords.	這是一隻「已故」的鸚鵡。牠喝多了精靈司令（其實只喝了一杯）。其實，牠只是在思念峽灣。
the parrot	鸚鵡
