the door to the Blue Parrot Inn	藍鸚鵡旅店的門
If the sign is correct, this is the stained and dirty door to the Blue Parrot Inn.	如果招牌沒錯，這扇滿是污漬又骯髒的門就是藍鸚鵡旅店的入口。
the sign of the Blue Parrot Inn	藍鸚鵡旅店的招牌
