After all the trouble you took to get your hands on that Raven, it's really a shame you couldn't take any more damage.  You should've tended to your healing, but now it's too late. 	你費了那麼大功夫才拿到那隻烏鴉，如今卻承受不住更多傷害，實在可惜。你早該治療傷勢，但現在已經太遲了。
Don't just stand there....	別愣在那裡……
the alley leading west	通往西方的小巷
